snippet.title: In Deppth Look At Johnny's $50M Lawsuit Against Narcissist Ex Amber Heard... He's Got Her Cornered!
snippet.description:
#INJOHNNYWETRUST

If you want a news channel that gets to the point, this isn't for you. This is THE DARTH NEWS EXPERIENCE. Welcome All 🥳

An in Depth Video discussing and reviewing over all of Johnny Depp's legal testimonies since 2016.  Regarding the "abuse allegations" by ex wife Amber Heard. 

Hopefully for those of you who are not following the story, you find this video entertaining , slightly offensive and informative. The point of my channel is NOT about getting to the point, but I always get there, eventually.. See my point?
